title: City of the Dead/Horror Hotel (1960)
description:
A young college student studying "Old Salem" witchcraft travels to the quiet New England town where, centuries earlier, a witch was burned at the stake. She finds that things are not as quiet as they appear, and soon she is the target of the coven that still exists there, searching for a sacrifice to offer to the devil on "Candlemass Eve".
